WEBVTT

01:52.870 --> 01:53.870
If it were poisoned,

01:53.870 --> 01:55.800
I would be the first to be poisoned.

01:56.070 --> 01:57.130
Then let me ask you,

01:58.229 --> 02:00.280
what about that string of Zhuyao?

02:11.590 --> 02:13.280
I really didn't eat it.

02:15.240 --> 02:17.400
But that is our custom in Changmo.

02:17.840 --> 02:19.240
When I brought it to you,

02:19.240 --> 02:20.840
it had been washed clean.

02:21.240 --> 02:23.040
There was nothing wrong with it.

02:24.430 --> 02:24.910
Your Majesty.

02:24.910 --> 02:25.510
All right.

02:28.030 --> 02:29.280
All right.

02:29.960 --> 02:31.470
I can suspect anyone,

02:32.680 --> 02:33.470
but I

02:34.870 --> 02:36.800
can't suspect my own Consort Ling.

02:39.240 --> 02:40.240
You look haggard.

02:41.680 --> 02:42.680
You must have...

02:44.470 --> 02:47.280
worried about my health lately.

02:49.590 --> 02:50.960
Let me help you rest.

02:50.960 --> 02:51.590
I'm...

02:51.590 --> 02:52.360
not tired.

03:13.030 --> 03:13.750
Let me

03:14.470 --> 03:15.680
tuck you in.

03:16.280 --> 03:18.480
Your Majesty, aren't you going to rest?

03:19.000 --> 03:20.400
I want to watch you sleep.

03:23.000 --> 03:24.120
Your Majesty,

03:24.120 --> 03:26.360
I have something important to report.

03:28.190 --> 03:29.520
You get some rest first.

03:29.840 --> 03:30.970
I will be right back.

03:42.910 --> 03:43.590
Your Majesty,

03:43.590 --> 03:45.800
what you wanted to investigate
is now clear.

03:45.800 --> 03:47.560
Huo Ran was indeed

03:47.560 --> 03:49.870
planted by the late Emperor
by Lord Fei's side

03:49.870 --> 03:51.190
to keep an eye on him.

03:53.430 --> 03:54.590
What did Huo Ran say?

03:54.840 --> 03:57.400
He said everything was fine before,

03:57.430 --> 03:58.310
but

03:58.310 --> 04:00.750
ever since he came back
from Tianlang Pass,

04:00.750 --> 04:03.190
Lord Fei has been acting a little strange.

04:05.120 --> 04:05.800
Okay.

04:06.400 --> 04:07.080
Got it.

04:15.150 --> 04:15.950
Your Majesty,

04:16.040 --> 04:18.630
aren't you going back to Consort Ling?

04:19.360 --> 04:20.690
With someone beside me,

04:21.480 --> 04:22.630
I can't sleep well.

04:41.950 --> 04:42.750
Jin Xi.

04:44.270 --> 04:45.070
Jin Xi.

04:49.270 --> 04:50.070
Hall Master.

04:51.000 --> 04:52.390
If she doesn't take the antidote soon,

04:52.390 --> 04:53.450
she won't survive.

04:54.680 --> 04:55.630
What did you say?

04:57.070 --> 04:59.000
Please grant her the antidote,
Hall Master.

04:59.000 --> 04:59.659
Otherwise,

04:59.830 --> 05:01.630
she won't even last half an hour.

05:02.070 --> 05:03.000
No rush.

05:03.560 --> 05:05.270
I want you to watch her

05:05.630 --> 05:08.430
suffer the consequences
of disobeying my orders.

05:08.870 --> 05:09.870
Does it pain you?

05:11.240 --> 05:12.190
Pain me?

05:16.000 --> 05:16.870
She lives

05:17.830 --> 05:18.830
merely because she remains useful

05:18.830 --> 05:19.830
in the palace.

05:20.270 --> 05:21.120
Otherwise,

05:21.480 --> 05:23.280
if I were by Liu Chu's side alone,

05:23.830 --> 05:25.630
I couldn't hold everything together.

05:25.630 --> 05:27.000
Now, you look a bit

05:27.000 --> 05:28.120
like a Changmo spy.

05:30.160 --> 05:30.950
Don't worry.

05:31.160 --> 05:32.480
I won't let her die.

05:32.830 --> 05:34.480
When your poison acts up,

05:35.560 --> 05:37.560
I'll have her watch you the same way.

05:42.070 --> 05:43.950
Hand over the real antidote.

05:45.480 --> 05:46.430
Do it.

05:46.920 --> 05:47.600
Kill me.

05:47.600 --> 05:49.060
You think I wouldn't dare?

05:51.600 --> 05:52.560
Kill me,

05:52.630 --> 05:54.760
and no one can control you two anymore.

05:55.040 --> 05:55.830
Oh, right,

05:56.560 --> 05:59.090
and no one will give you
the antidote anymore.

05:59.480 --> 06:01.680
Then you two will hold each other,

06:02.070 --> 06:03.750
suffering a fate worse than death.

06:03.750 --> 06:06.010
Just thinking about it makes me so happy.

06:20.680 --> 06:21.480
I have lain hidden in Jinglan

06:21.480 --> 06:22.750
for so many years.

06:23.750 --> 06:24.750
I don't even remember

06:24.750 --> 06:26.160
how much I've suffered.

06:26.560 --> 06:28.160
Now I am atop all ministerial ranks.

06:28.160 --> 06:28.950
But you?

06:29.680 --> 06:31.010
You have never shown up.

06:31.800 --> 06:33.000
I am human too.

06:33.480 --> 06:34.480
So what?

06:34.480 --> 06:36.480
You will always be a pawn of Changmo.

06:36.480 --> 06:38.630
I have never forgotten my identity.

06:39.390 --> 06:40.680
For all these years,

06:40.830 --> 06:41.870
in all I do,

06:42.360 --> 06:44.960
I have taken Changmo's
grand mission as my own.

06:48.070 --> 06:50.870
So I beg you, Hall Master,
to grant me the antidote,

06:51.480 --> 06:52.510
so Jin Xi

06:53.390 --> 06:54.870
can lend me a hand.

06:59.800 --> 07:01.070
She is my subordinate.

07:01.240 --> 07:02.900
I naturally won't let her die.

07:03.160 --> 07:04.750
But when your poison acts up,

07:04.750 --> 07:06.240
whether you can find me

07:07.480 --> 07:09.160
depends on your luck.

07:10.870 --> 07:12.200
Thank you, Hall Master.

07:12.630 --> 07:13.430
You may leave.

07:13.870 --> 07:14.480
Yes.

07:20.390 --> 07:21.800
He has feelings for you.

07:22.680 --> 07:23.950
Then it seems

07:23.950 --> 07:25.350
you are still of some use.

07:34.830 --> 07:35.920
It's useless.

07:36.950 --> 07:38.610
Even if he has feelings for me,

07:39.000 --> 07:40.190
it's useless.

07:43.040 --> 07:44.570
Whether it's useful or not,

07:45.040 --> 07:46.560
we'll know once we try.

07:54.159 --> 07:55.070
Lord Zhang.

07:59.040 --> 08:00.070
How are you today?

08:00.750 --> 08:02.410
I've been waiting for so long,

08:02.630 --> 08:04.750
and you've finally come.

08:05.390 --> 08:06.990
How did you know I would come?

08:07.070 --> 08:08.630
I thought

08:08.630 --> 08:10.830
His Majesty would remember our old ties

08:11.070 --> 08:14.000
and come to see me one last time.

08:14.390 --> 08:16.870
I didn't expect it to be you.

08:17.240 --> 08:18.680
It's good that it's you.

08:19.190 --> 08:20.390
Now that you are here,

08:21.480 --> 08:23.750
I can finally drink this pot of wine

08:25.120 --> 08:27.510
with peace of mind.

08:32.240 --> 08:34.240
Thank you for visiting me.

08:39.270 --> 08:40.240
Lord Zhang.

08:41.440 --> 08:43.669
You ending up like this

08:44.360 --> 08:46.240
is entirely your own doing.

08:46.840 --> 08:47.960
General Xiao,

08:48.200 --> 08:51.360
do you really think I would
secretly keep a dragon robe?

08:51.670 --> 08:54.440
Do you really think I would rebel?

08:55.240 --> 08:56.360
Actually,

08:56.600 --> 08:59.030
His Majesty knows everything.

08:59.630 --> 09:01.080
Li Shichang

09:01.080 --> 09:02.670
is framing me up.

09:02.670 --> 09:05.390
Then why would His Majesty punish you?

09:11.480 --> 09:13.840
Because His Majesty has grown up,

09:14.030 --> 09:15.960
and he doesn't need me anymore.

09:16.080 --> 09:18.150
And these trumped-up charges

09:18.150 --> 09:21.360
are the best excuse to get rid of me.

09:21.670 --> 09:23.030
General Xiao,

09:23.030 --> 09:24.630
you are smart and wise.

09:24.960 --> 09:26.360
How could you not know?

09:26.360 --> 09:28.080
Why bother asking?

09:29.550 --> 09:31.610
Even if you had no intention to rebel,

09:31.960 --> 09:32.750
Lord Zhang,

09:33.550 --> 09:35.150
how do you explain

09:35.360 --> 09:36.840
the Huangpi Village incident?

09:36.840 --> 09:38.670
So the annihilation

09:38.670 --> 09:40.600
of my entire family

09:40.960 --> 09:43.360
has atoned for their lives.

09:44.750 --> 09:46.870
Even if there's a slight risk,

09:47.480 --> 09:50.150
I couldn't let the tragedy
from 8 years ago

09:50.320 --> 09:52.080
happen again.

09:55.390 --> 09:56.390
Eight years ago?

10:03.790 --> 10:05.030
General Xiao.

10:05.670 --> 10:08.000
A strange disease 8 years ago

10:08.000 --> 10:09.670
turned the whole Jinglan

10:09.670 --> 10:12.030
into a living hell.

10:13.240 --> 10:14.320
My son

10:15.150 --> 10:16.670
also caught the disease.

10:17.390 --> 10:20.520
Although the Han family
tried their best to save people,

10:21.030 --> 10:23.600
many still died.

10:23.750 --> 10:25.960
Finally, the disease stabilized.

10:26.360 --> 10:28.200
I thought my son

10:28.200 --> 10:29.600
could survive.

10:30.960 --> 10:31.910
Unexpectedly,

10:33.030 --> 10:35.890
after taking a dose of medicine
from the Han family,

10:36.670 --> 10:38.870
he suddenly died.

10:39.750 --> 10:40.630
So,

10:41.270 --> 10:43.530
you hated the Han family because of this.

10:44.480 --> 10:46.740
Han Yunling was in danger several times.

10:47.480 --> 10:48.200
Lord Zhang,

10:48.510 --> 10:50.110
it was all your doing, right?

10:51.080 --> 10:52.030
That's right.

10:53.000 --> 10:54.240
It was me.

10:55.030 --> 10:56.030
From the moment Han Yunling

10:56.030 --> 10:58.080
stepped into Jinglan,

10:59.080 --> 11:01.870
I sent people
to assassinate her every day.

11:02.200 --> 11:02.840
If it weren't for you,

11:02.840 --> 11:05.870
I would have avenged my son long ago.

11:06.270 --> 11:08.630
But the prescription
was not written by Han Yunling.

11:08.630 --> 11:09.440
Lord Zhang,

11:09.960 --> 11:11.240
she is innocent.

11:11.480 --> 11:12.870
What about my son?

11:13.550 --> 11:15.390
How innocent was he!

11:19.080 --> 11:20.360
I also know

11:22.480 --> 11:24.870
I can't entirely blame the Han family.

11:25.870 --> 11:26.960
But I

11:28.240 --> 11:30.440
only had this one son.

11:33.270 --> 11:33.790
I...

11:37.270 --> 11:40.270
I have hatred in my heart!

11:42.000 --> 11:43.480
I hate them!

11:52.030 --> 11:53.270
When

11:53.550 --> 11:54.670
I was young,

11:55.030 --> 11:58.230
I followed the late Emperor
in campaigns across the land.

11:58.360 --> 12:00.270
After the late Emperor passed away,

12:00.270 --> 12:02.870
I've devoted myself
to assisting His Majesty,

12:03.270 --> 12:05.000
fulfilling my duties

12:05.030 --> 12:06.960
and serving the people wholeheartedly.

12:06.960 --> 12:08.630
With my assistance,

12:08.870 --> 12:11.240
Jinglan has become even more prosperous.

12:11.630 --> 12:13.360
If annihilating the Han family

12:13.630 --> 12:15.890
is me abusing my power for personal gain,

12:16.240 --> 12:17.080
then

12:18.080 --> 12:20.600
I'll own this one and only stain

12:21.720 --> 12:23.200
on my life.

12:28.000 --> 12:28.660
Lord Zhang.

12:29.080 --> 12:30.150
General Xiao.

12:31.550 --> 12:33.150
Do you know who sent you

12:33.390 --> 12:36.080
to Tianlang Pass back then?

12:37.480 --> 12:38.630
It was me.

12:38.960 --> 12:42.030
When Changmo attacked with a massive army,

12:42.240 --> 12:44.080
Tianlang Pass was on the verge of falling.

12:44.080 --> 12:45.390
The frontline desperately needed a capable

12:45.390 --> 12:47.600
and loyal military general.

12:47.670 --> 12:48.870
You and Fei Zheng

12:49.030 --> 12:51.000
were both close to His Majesty.

12:51.080 --> 12:53.390
Fei Zheng was also very capable.

12:54.030 --> 12:55.750
But I always felt

12:56.390 --> 12:57.960
that Fei Zheng

12:58.600 --> 13:01.150
harbored an unspeakable secret.

13:01.670 --> 13:03.360
So I resolutely

13:03.360 --> 13:04.670
sent you.

13:04.960 --> 13:07.440
You indeed did not let me down.

13:07.960 --> 13:08.790
However,

13:09.790 --> 13:12.390
your interference
in the Han family's affairs

13:13.480 --> 13:15.960
forced me to eliminate you.

13:18.550 --> 13:19.440
So it seems

13:20.150 --> 13:22.000
the poisoned dart incident
in Huangpi Village

13:22.000 --> 13:23.270
was also your doing.

13:23.670 --> 13:24.670
That's right.

13:25.750 --> 13:26.870
It was me.

13:34.000 --> 13:36.550
It is all over.

13:43.790 --> 13:46.750
Seeing you and Fei Zheng
build your careers

13:46.750 --> 13:48.680
and receive great imperial grace,

13:49.600 --> 13:52.870
I think of my dead son.

13:54.000 --> 13:56.030
If he were still alive,

13:57.200 --> 13:59.030
he would be just like you,

14:00.840 --> 14:04.360
a pillar of Jinglan,

14:05.670 --> 14:06.870
wouldn't he?

14:09.000 --> 14:09.660
Lord Zhang.

14:11.840 --> 14:13.370
Let me have a drink with you.

14:14.000 --> 14:15.150
General Xiao,

14:16.670 --> 14:17.870
thank you.

14:19.440 --> 14:21.870
Thank you for coming to see me today.

14:24.030 --> 14:25.670
Only I am qualified

14:28.360 --> 14:30.270
to drink

14:31.080 --> 14:32.200
this pot of wine.

14:34.240 --> 14:35.240
Son,

14:37.480 --> 14:40.030
we will meet soon anyway.

14:42.670 --> 14:43.330
Lord Zhang.

14:44.390 --> 14:45.870
Lord Zhang!

14:46.360 --> 14:47.080
Lord Zhang!

14:48.480 --> 14:49.240
Lord Zhang.

14:50.550 --> 14:51.240
Guards!

14:53.670 --> 14:54.790
General Xiao,

14:56.480 --> 14:57.750
remember this.

14:57.870 --> 14:58.840
His Majesty

14:59.510 --> 15:00.910
has become

15:00.910 --> 15:03.440
a meticulous emperor.

15:04.150 --> 15:06.030
When serving an emperor,

15:06.630 --> 15:08.360
men may easily share hardship,

15:09.200 --> 15:10.840
but not

15:12.080 --> 15:12.870
prosperity.

15:13.480 --> 15:14.240
Lord Zhang.

15:14.960 --> 15:15.790
Lord Zhang.

15:16.000 --> 15:17.440
Why must you do this?

15:19.030 --> 15:20.670
I prided myself all my life

15:21.600 --> 15:23.750
on being upright and innocent.

15:25.480 --> 15:27.960
But I have also done many wrong things.

15:28.870 --> 15:31.870
Even if His Majesty granted me mercy,

15:33.630 --> 15:35.480
I would have no desire...

15:37.630 --> 15:38.440
Lord Zhang.

15:39.080 --> 15:40.000
Guards!

15:41.360 --> 15:42.080
To stay...

15:46.750 --> 15:49.480
to stay in this world.

15:52.750 --> 15:53.550
Lord Zhang.

15:53.910 --> 15:54.870
Lord Zhang.

15:55.670 --> 15:57.030
Guards!

16:00.440 --> 16:02.270
Physician Han Yunling,

16:02.270 --> 16:03.870
with her sincere heart

16:03.870 --> 16:05.480
and exquisite skills,

16:05.480 --> 16:07.870
is truly a model for physicians.

16:08.030 --> 16:10.390
She is hereby awarded 100 taels of gold

16:10.390 --> 16:12.240
and 10 bolts of brocade

16:12.240 --> 16:14.030
to honor her contributions.

16:14.240 --> 16:16.240
Thus decreed.

16:17.840 --> 16:19.630
Thank you for the reward, Your Majesty.

16:19.630 --> 16:21.790
I only did my duty as a physician.

16:22.630 --> 16:23.360
You may rise.

16:23.870 --> 16:25.270
Thank you, Your Majesty.

16:25.790 --> 16:28.200
Fei Zheng has served at court
for many years,

16:28.200 --> 16:29.960
diligently fulfilling his duties

16:29.960 --> 16:32.270
and promoting etiquette.

16:32.480 --> 16:33.670
From now on,

16:33.790 --> 16:35.440
Fei Zheng is relieved of his post

16:35.440 --> 16:37.600
as Minister of Revenue

16:37.630 --> 16:39.600
and appointed as Minister of Rites

16:39.600 --> 16:41.840
to focus on managing
the Ministry of Rites.

16:41.840 --> 16:43.670
Thus decreed.

16:47.030 --> 16:48.160
I accept the decree.

16:49.270 --> 16:51.960
The affairs of the Ministry of Rites
are complex.

16:51.960 --> 16:55.000
From now on, just focus on
managing the Ministry of Rites.

16:55.000 --> 16:55.670
I believe

16:56.270 --> 16:58.480
you will convince all the officials.

17:01.390 --> 17:03.240
-Your Majesty, you're wise.
-Your Majesty, you're wise.

17:03.240 --> 17:05.770
-We bow in admiration.
-We bow in admiration.

17:08.640 --> 17:09.569
Gold and silver,

17:09.920 --> 17:10.790
properties,

17:11.270 --> 17:13.880
and taxes from the border fiefs.

17:28.830 --> 17:30.030
Logically speaking,

17:30.030 --> 17:32.030
Your Majesty, since you just
recovered from a serious illness

17:32.030 --> 17:34.240
and eliminated hidden dangers
in the court,

17:34.240 --> 17:35.960
rewarding these meritorious officials

17:35.960 --> 17:36.880
is inevitable.

17:37.270 --> 17:40.240
However,
regarding the taxes of border fiefs...

17:42.440 --> 17:44.400
there has never been such a system.

17:45.350 --> 17:46.440
Xie,

17:47.030 --> 17:48.480
Fei Zheng and Xiao Chi

17:49.030 --> 17:51.290
are not only retainers who grew up with me

17:51.680 --> 17:53.440
but also important officials in the court

17:53.440 --> 17:54.790
that I must rely on.

17:55.000 --> 17:57.000
How can I not give them more rewards?

17:57.030 --> 17:57.920
What's more,

17:58.310 --> 18:00.240
Han Yunling even saved my life.

18:01.030 --> 18:03.480
If it were you who got sick,

18:04.030 --> 18:04.640
what

18:05.270 --> 18:06.400
would you do?

18:09.160 --> 18:10.550
If I were the one sick,

18:11.070 --> 18:13.400
rewarding this much silver
would be enough.

18:13.400 --> 18:15.270
But they saved you, Your Majesty.

18:17.480 --> 18:19.350
They must be heavily rewarded.

18:19.830 --> 18:20.480
Very well.

18:20.790 --> 18:21.640
Tomorrow,

18:21.640 --> 18:23.680
I will have someone take these things

18:23.680 --> 18:25.160
out of the treasury

18:25.160 --> 18:26.200
and send them over.

18:26.200 --> 18:29.240
As for the taxes from the border fiefs,

18:29.830 --> 18:31.880
we can only wait
until after the autumn harvest

18:31.880 --> 18:33.590
to escort the silver back to the capital.

18:33.590 --> 18:34.680
Only after it enters the treasury

18:34.680 --> 18:36.280
can we give further rewards.

18:37.160 --> 18:37.690
Alright.

18:38.070 --> 18:40.000
I'll listen to you, Xie.

18:40.960 --> 18:41.560
By the way,

18:41.920 --> 18:43.050
for all these years,

18:43.240 --> 18:45.830
I've known nothing about the treasury.

18:45.830 --> 18:46.790
Xie,

18:46.790 --> 18:48.880
could you give me the treasury ledgers

18:48.880 --> 18:49.790
to take a look?

18:53.270 --> 18:55.480
You used to be completely uninterested

18:56.160 --> 18:57.480
in these things.

18:57.880 --> 18:58.790
Today...

19:01.070 --> 19:02.480
what has gotten into you?

19:03.640 --> 19:04.830
As a ruler,

19:05.310 --> 19:06.920
I should be familiar with

19:07.200 --> 19:08.800
all the affairs of the state.

19:09.270 --> 19:11.600
After all, they are the treasury ledgers.

19:11.750 --> 19:12.880
And I remember,

19:13.310 --> 19:15.170
when our father was on the throne,

19:15.590 --> 19:17.160
he seemed never to have handed

19:17.160 --> 19:18.360
the treasury ledgers

19:18.590 --> 19:19.640
to anyone else,

19:20.030 --> 19:20.640
right?

19:22.510 --> 19:23.160
Yes.

19:26.200 --> 19:29.400
Our father was a wise and valiant man.

19:30.200 --> 19:31.070
Back then,

19:31.070 --> 19:32.590
he executed the brothers
who fought alongside him

19:32.590 --> 19:34.240
to conquer the empire

19:34.880 --> 19:36.480
just to secure his throne.

19:44.960 --> 19:47.020
I don't know about these things, Xie.

19:47.310 --> 19:48.570
I was still young then.

19:48.590 --> 19:49.720
You must know

19:49.920 --> 19:51.850
these situations better than I do.

19:52.160 --> 19:53.510
I just want

19:53.720 --> 19:55.270
to learn about the ledgers.

19:55.680 --> 19:56.480
Xie,

19:56.830 --> 19:58.360
please don't overthink it.

19:58.790 --> 19:59.750
Of course not.

20:00.550 --> 20:01.510
Tomorrow, I will have someone

20:01.510 --> 20:03.200
send the treasury ledgers
from all these years

20:03.200 --> 20:04.270
to you.

20:04.270 --> 20:04.790
Really?

20:07.400 --> 20:08.590
You still don't trust me.

20:08.590 --> 20:10.640
How could I not trust you?

20:10.750 --> 20:12.880
You are the person I trust the most.

20:13.680 --> 20:14.400
Xie,

20:14.550 --> 20:16.030
my ear is itching again.

20:16.070 --> 20:18.070
Could you give me an ear cleaning?

20:19.270 --> 20:20.000
Sure.

20:20.350 --> 20:21.400
Bring the tools.

20:30.510 --> 20:31.110
Oh, right.

20:31.790 --> 20:33.030
I just remembered.

20:34.400 --> 20:36.640
I haven't had my afternoon medicine yet.

20:36.640 --> 20:37.900
If I don't go back soon,

20:38.590 --> 20:40.790
the poison in my body might act up again.

20:40.830 --> 20:41.960
Then I will

20:41.960 --> 20:42.880
take my leave.

20:55.400 --> 20:57.880
Are we really going
to send the ledgers over?

20:59.480 --> 21:01.410
Today, he wants to see the ledgers.

21:01.880 --> 21:04.880
Tomorrow, he will want
to take back the treasury keys.

21:05.400 --> 21:06.750
First it was Wang Ruhai.

21:06.750 --> 21:08.030
Then it was Lord Zhang.

21:08.270 --> 21:10.070
Now, even Fei Zheng, close to him,

21:10.070 --> 21:13.400
has been transferred
to a sinecure in the Ministry of Rites.

21:15.240 --> 21:16.000
And

21:16.400 --> 21:18.030
the ruthlessness in his eyes

21:19.160 --> 21:21.960
is just like our father's back then.

21:25.550 --> 21:26.200
Then,

21:26.510 --> 21:27.200
we...

21:27.790 --> 21:29.240
He killed key ministers

21:31.400 --> 21:32.590
and seized power.

21:34.160 --> 21:35.400
It seems Liu Chu

21:35.400 --> 21:37.260
is completely out of control now.

21:38.680 --> 21:40.270
Rather than await death,

21:41.960 --> 21:43.640
I must strike first.

21:46.680 --> 21:47.940
Notify Xieying Guard.

21:48.480 --> 21:50.540
Tomorrow at the Princess's Mansion,

21:51.310 --> 21:53.370
I will host a banquet for His Majesty.

21:55.680 --> 21:56.480
Yes.

22:00.000 --> 22:00.880
You're here.

22:03.640 --> 22:04.550
What's wrong?

22:04.550 --> 22:05.880
Something on your mind?

22:09.640 --> 22:10.960
Lord Zhang is dead.

22:13.790 --> 22:16.400
Didn't he deserve it?

22:17.400 --> 22:19.060
Although we didn't get along,

22:19.640 --> 22:20.880
I only now realize

22:21.640 --> 22:23.440
he wasn't actually a bad person.

22:23.640 --> 22:24.720
He was even

22:24.720 --> 22:26.980
an indispensable minister in the court.

22:27.240 --> 22:28.830
Even though he was a stubborn old man,

22:28.830 --> 22:30.430
he was devoted to the country

22:30.510 --> 22:31.440
and His Majesty.

22:32.640 --> 22:35.040
Then why did he
secretly keep a dragon robe?

22:35.480 --> 22:36.750
He didn't explain.

22:37.070 --> 22:38.070
But I feel like

22:38.590 --> 22:40.320
it's not something he would do.

22:42.350 --> 22:43.590
He's dead anyway.

22:44.160 --> 22:45.400
Don't overthink it.

22:46.750 --> 22:47.590
Yeah.

22:48.590 --> 22:49.680
He is dead.

22:50.070 --> 22:51.240
All past grievances

22:51.830 --> 22:53.230
should come to an end too.

23:04.640 --> 23:06.000
About what happened back then,

23:06.000 --> 23:08.130
do you really remember nothing at all?

23:11.590 --> 23:13.320
It seems the old saying is true.

23:15.400 --> 23:16.400
What old saying?

23:17.160 --> 23:19.290
"A physician can't heal themselves."

23:20.640 --> 23:21.790
You even know that.

23:23.680 --> 23:26.010
Since a physician can't heal themselves,

23:27.000 --> 23:28.660
I'll find someone to heal you.

23:37.480 --> 23:39.830
Physician Han, your pulse is stable.

23:39.830 --> 23:41.270
It shows no abnormalities.

23:41.270 --> 23:43.790
As for the memory loss you mentioned,

23:43.880 --> 23:45.680
there is nothing I can do.

23:58.030 --> 23:58.830
Physician.

24:00.160 --> 24:01.420
Will this really work?

24:03.790 --> 24:05.520
Have you remembered anything?

24:14.480 --> 24:15.000
Then...

24:15.440 --> 24:16.750
I'm out of ideas.

24:17.000 --> 24:18.200
Hurry up and come out.

24:26.590 --> 24:27.400
Han Yunling.

24:27.880 --> 24:29.070
Spirits of heaven.

24:29.350 --> 24:31.160
Spirits of heaven and earth.

24:31.160 --> 24:32.920
Ancestor Bodhisattva, please manifest.

24:32.920 --> 24:34.590
Please manifest.

24:38.550 --> 24:39.550
You actually believe this?

24:39.550 --> 24:40.830
Just giving it a try.

24:41.480 --> 24:43.030
Spirits of heaven and earth.

24:43.030 --> 24:45.360
Ancestor Bodhisattva, please manifest.

24:45.440 --> 24:46.720
Please manifest.

24:51.880 --> 24:52.400
Chu.

24:55.790 --> 24:56.590
Your Majesty.

24:59.640 --> 25:00.790
Zheng, you're here.

25:01.750 --> 25:03.350
There are no outsiders here.

25:03.440 --> 25:05.030
Why the formal greeting?

25:05.030 --> 25:05.920
Please, rise.

25:06.270 --> 25:06.880
Yes.

25:08.880 --> 25:10.830
I asked you to manage
the Ministry of Rites earlier.

25:10.830 --> 25:11.960
Do you have any objections?

25:11.960 --> 25:13.640
It was your arrangement.

25:13.960 --> 25:15.640
Naturally, I will obey.

25:16.400 --> 25:18.270
Besides, the Ministry of Revenue

25:18.480 --> 25:19.880
is full of tedious tasks.

25:20.000 --> 25:21.860
I have long thought of resigning.

25:23.680 --> 25:24.480
Good.

25:26.480 --> 25:27.610
Rites and etiquette

25:28.160 --> 25:30.030
are Jinglan's dignity.

25:30.400 --> 25:32.260
I can't trust anyone else with it.

25:32.590 --> 25:33.990
Only by trusting it to you

25:34.440 --> 25:35.880
can I feel at ease.

25:37.030 --> 25:38.000
I will keep

25:38.270 --> 25:40.270
your words in mind.

25:43.270 --> 25:44.680
I just remembered.

25:45.030 --> 25:46.790
Before you came to the Prince's Mansion,

25:46.790 --> 25:49.120
you were a hunter in the mountains, right?

25:51.000 --> 25:52.660
In a few days, when we are free,

25:52.750 --> 25:55.080
you and Xiao Chi
will accompany me to hunt.

26:00.160 --> 26:00.960
Yes.

26:01.400 --> 26:02.880
My father was indeed

26:02.880 --> 26:04.480
the best hunter in the village.

26:04.480 --> 26:05.440
It's a pity

26:05.960 --> 26:07.440
that he passed away too early.

26:07.440 --> 26:09.700
I didn't manage to learn hunting skills.

26:11.880 --> 26:13.400
After your father died,

26:13.550 --> 26:15.550
did you enter the Prince's Mansion?

26:17.200 --> 26:18.800
After my father passed away,

26:19.000 --> 26:19.790
I was helpless

26:19.790 --> 26:21.320
and ended up on the streets.

26:21.550 --> 26:23.480
Later, I was abducted
by human traffickers.

26:23.480 --> 26:24.480
But fortunately,

26:24.920 --> 26:26.750
I was sold to the Prince's Mansion.

26:26.750 --> 26:27.830
That's how I met you

26:27.830 --> 26:28.640
and Chi.

26:31.790 --> 26:33.270
Zheng.

26:35.270 --> 26:36.030
Look,

26:36.640 --> 26:37.880
you and Xiao Chi

26:38.240 --> 26:40.100
both came from poor backgrounds.

26:40.680 --> 26:41.480
But now?

26:42.160 --> 26:43.680
One is the Minister of Rites,

26:43.680 --> 26:46.200
and the other is a provincial viceroy.

26:46.440 --> 26:49.750
And you are as close as my own brothers.

26:51.480 --> 26:53.030
What a great story.

26:53.550 --> 26:56.270
It will surely be recorded
in the history books,

26:56.640 --> 26:58.160
praised by everyone,

26:58.640 --> 27:00.500
and passed down for generations.

27:03.480 --> 27:04.940
You are absolutely right.

27:06.030 --> 27:07.000
That I

27:07.510 --> 27:08.710
can be where I am today

27:09.880 --> 27:11.810
is all thanks to your cultivation.

27:18.790 --> 27:19.590
Your Majesty,

27:19.790 --> 27:21.590
tomorrow is the 15th of September,

27:21.590 --> 27:22.550
the night of the full moon.

27:22.550 --> 27:23.720
Her Highness is going to host a banquet

27:23.720 --> 27:25.980
and invites you to her mansion for a chat.

27:26.590 --> 27:27.400
All right.

27:28.160 --> 27:30.090
I will definitely be there on time.

27:30.790 --> 27:31.590
Zheng.

27:32.480 --> 27:33.740
Tomorrow is a good day.

27:33.880 --> 27:34.640
How about

27:35.160 --> 27:36.880
you and Xiao Chi come with me?

27:37.960 --> 27:38.550
Chu,

27:39.160 --> 27:39.750
then...

27:42.880 --> 27:44.480
I think I'll pass.

27:45.400 --> 27:46.240
You know,

27:46.480 --> 27:47.960
I just took office
in the Ministry of Rites,

27:47.960 --> 27:50.160
and there are many matters to hand over.

27:50.480 --> 27:51.790
I also have a lot of documents

27:51.790 --> 27:53.050
and case files to read.

27:53.400 --> 27:53.960
I...

27:54.830 --> 27:56.230
I think I'll just skip it.

27:59.750 --> 28:00.880
That's fine too.

28:01.680 --> 28:02.920
Then I expect

28:03.550 --> 28:06.070
you to achieve something
in the Ministry of Rites

28:06.070 --> 28:08.880
by promoting etiquette in the court,

28:09.030 --> 28:10.830
to be an example for the ministers

28:10.830 --> 28:12.760
and a role model for all officials.

28:18.750 --> 28:19.440
I

28:19.750 --> 28:20.810
accept the decree.

28:47.440 --> 28:49.170
The Eldest Princess's person?

28:50.480 --> 28:52.810
She left the palace secretly at this time.

29:08.270 --> 29:10.550
I've had amnesia for so many years.

29:10.550 --> 29:12.640
It won't be easy to recover my memory.

29:17.030 --> 29:18.640
There must be another way.

29:22.030 --> 29:22.880
Forget it.

29:25.880 --> 29:26.920
Things are fine

29:27.400 --> 29:28.330
the way they are.

31:15.790 --> 31:17.030
General, His Majesty has an urgent matter

31:17.030 --> 31:17.880
and summons you back to the palace.
